description:
On the island of Mona, the young Taran gradually regaining strength after having nearly died in the storm.

But forced to land on Scotland, they encounter the clan of the Pictish. The druid Leuweg, asked for help to regain the stone of destiny that has stolen by a Viking tribe. Leuweg who sees beyond appearances, certify that the quest for the cauldron of Dagda is related to the stone. Gwenc'hlan agrees to help the clan and all leave to Iceland to fight the Vikings. But not far behind, helped by a fellow, Gwenc'hlan
name: The Stone of Destiny

description:
Brother Thomas has just been murdered in the heart of the city of Is.

he translated an extract that would reveal the location where two Celtic talismans were hidden. Talwrc'h, the Pictish chief, under the influence of divine beverage, formerly prophesied where his people should keep these talismans.

The Cauldron of Dagda who gives knowledge and who raises the warriors. And the spear of Lugh, the magic spear of 5 points, that never fails ...

Gwenc'hlan is back and has to solve a murder case. But is it so simple?

No, because this case is covered in dark maneuvers to grab the secrets of the druids and make off with the city of Is. The church of Rome works behind the scenes ...

At the turn of this case, Gwenc'hlan the druid and his young apprentice are in search of truth.
name: The Discussion of the giants

description: Brother Thomas has just been murdered in the heart of the city of Is. He translated an extract that would reveal where two Celtic talismans were hidden. Talwrc'h, the Pictish leader, while under the influence of divine beverage, formerly prophesied where his people had to keep these talismans: the cauldron of Dagda, who gives knowledge and who raises the warriors, and the spear of Lugh the magic spear of 5 points, that never fails ... Gwenc'hlan is back and must solve this case. But is it so simple? This case cover dark maneuvers to capture the secrets of the druids and make off with the city of Is. Indeed, the Church of Rome working in the shadows ... At the turn of this case, Gwenc'hlan the druid is in search of truth.
name: The spear of Lugh

description: At the time when Christianity supplanted the Celtic beliefs in Britain, Druids and monks come together to solve a series of ritual murders.
name: Le mystère des Oghams

description:
Fifth century. Slowly but surely, a shadow covers Gwenc'hlan, one of the last Druids, and his apprentice, Taran. Both are continuing to investigate the mystery surrounding what drives the rocky promontories of Brittany.

Needs of the investigation lead to the magnificent city of Is reign on which the beautiful and rebellious Dahud ... It is here that the mysteries of a vast conspiracy will unravel.
name: Is the white

volume.name: Charles Starrett as The Durango Kid

person_credits.name: Colin Upton
person_credits.role: writer, penciler, letterer, inker, colorist, cover

description: Charles Biro’s long-running star of Lev Gleason’s Boy Comics returns in a spectacular return performance of some of his best stories from comics’ Golden Age. “The Big Blast” is drawn by future Joe Kubert partner and Three Stooges producer Norman Maurer, as C.B. breaks up a gang using boobytrapped T. V.’s as murder weapons. “Spectators Also Die”, by Biro and Willian (Steve Roper)Overgard has C. B. sorting out a love triangle between Buzzy, Joanie and Scooter. Buzzy ends up dead. “The Turtles’ Secret”,by Charles Biro has Crimebuster and his sometimes-partner Squeeks the Monkey on the trail of $25,000,000.00 in pirate treasure, and “Emergency Chute Failed” (By Biro and Overgard) has C. B. and Squeeks sorting out a fixed air race. Every story is lovingly restored and reprinted as cleanly as the day it went to press . Stories are from Boy Illostories #’s 79, 99, and 103. Color cover by Biro, interiors are black and white. Standard comic format.

It’s the epilogue to “The Court of Owls”!

The next major storyline begins here!
name: Ghost in the Machine;

description: The finale of the fight with TERMINUS!
name: Terminus Last Gasp

description:
BATGIRL battles BATWOMAN!

KNIGHTFALL strikes!
name: Every Time I Fail

description:
THE SQUAD’S traitor is revealed!

BASILISK takes the fight to AMANDA WALLER’S home turf!
name: Killin' Time

description:
Hunt for Lobo part 4, The final battle with Lobo by writer/artist ROB LIEFELD!

Lobo has started the World Breaker Protocol, and has beaten Slade almost to death. Slade retreats with a plan and Lobo is forced to battle Tigorr and Primus. It is revealed that Primus was the one to free Lobo in the first place, because only Lobo knew where the Starpoint ship was hidden and how to start the engines. Primus also reveals that he turned off the World Breaker. Zealot over hears this and is furious with Primus for his trechery in freeing Lobo, but Primus tries to explain that Maxim isn't as nice as he apppears. This distraction makes it so Lobo can escape Primus's phyic grip. He doesn't get far, because Slade runs him down with Lobo's flying motorcycle and fly the pair skyward. There the two fight and Slade is able to jet pack away as Lobo and his motorcycle explode. Feeling Lobo is truly dead, Slade returns to Maxim for his payment. He also threatens Maxim that if he ever hurts Zealot, he's have to deal with Slade, then leaves Zealot with a parting kiss.

Later back at Maxim lab, it is revealed that Lobo's love, Sheba is still being held prisoner, and alive.
name: The Omega Agenda

description:
THE DEMON KNIGHTS are helpless in the clutches of MORGAINE LE FEY!

Even worse, they’ve already given her exactly what she needs to become the planet’s most powerful magician!

The road to a new Camelot will lead them to the last place you’d ever expect...
name: The Avalon Trap

description:
The conclusion of “SON OF SATAN’S RING”!

The mole inside S.H.A.D.E. is revealed.
name: Son of Satan's Ring, Pt. 3: To the Grave

description: Face-off with HELLSPONT!
name: Last Shot

description:
The team devises a plan to save their future by staying alive in the present!

Will they survive the fight against the METAMERICAN and THE METAMARINES, or lose the battle against each other?
name: A Prophecy of Death

description: Mitch meets the person who’s been pulling the strings of his misfortunes since issue #1!
name: The Reborn Identity

description:
There’s a monster hiding in the shadows of New York after dark, and she’s set her sights on Superboy. But her interest in him is more complicated than it seems!

Superboy’s just starting to figure out what it means to have friends – does he have the good judgment to pick the right ones? Or is he destined to run with the wrong crowd?
name: Night Games!

description:
Betrayal, revelations, blood, and DEATH come to the group as some find themselves powerless to the seductive charms and horrific powers of BROTHER BLOOD.

RIDGE is prepared as a blood sacrifice to indoctrinate the newest members of Brother Blood’s cult.

NOT everyone will survive this fatal encounter.
name: Unchained

description: “Why not just kill me now and be done with it?” And don’t miss the latest chapter of the CRIMSON CORSAIR backup epic from writer LEN WEIN and artist JOHN HIGGINS!
name: The Hand that Mocked Them...!; The Curse of the Crimson Corsair: The Devil in the Deep, Part Ten

description: Tarkan goes on a dangerous journey under the command of Attila the Hun ,to find the Sword of Mars that brings ultimate powers to it's holder.He travels bizarre lands and fights strange warriors and creatures on his way to the ultimate sword.
name: Sword of Mars (Mars'ın Kılıcı)

description: The original run of Marvel's G.I. JOE: A Real American Hero comes to a conclusion! Issues #146-155 are collected in this final volume of classic G.I. JOE. The Star Brigade teams up with the Oktober Guard, the JOEs plan a strike against Castle Destro, and a brainwashed Baroness, Billy, and Storm Shadow go up against Snake-Eyes, all leading up to the final issue. In issue #155, writer Larry Hama turns to his most celebrated character, Snake-Eyes - letting the ninja have his "say" - and gives these Real American Heroes the send-off they deserve.
name: Volume 15

description:
"CHANGEMENT"

Having experienced what he is truly up against, Alan will have to do the seemingly impossible to save Quinn from the assassin. The temperature continues to fall in Dresden--but when daylight rises, it is like the lights of a stage, and two dancers ready for a final performance.
name: Changement

description: In a remote village in the Aleutian Islands, the crew of theKapital, on the run from Siberian pirates, reconsiders their core mission as pacifists and conservationists. In this unpredictable and often violent world, should they be more? Narratives and story lines converge as the past catches up with the present, and in quiet, unassuming Unalaska, USA, a new mission is forged.
name: Landfall, Part 3: Unalaska

description:
THIS BOOK IS EXACTLY WHAT IT SOUNDS LIKE!

PUNISHER VS. THE HULK IN SPACE!

What if everthing you thought was funny about Deadpool…was actually just disturbing?

What if he decided to kill everyone and everything that makes up the Marvel Universe?

What if he actually pulled it off? Would that be FUN for you?

The Merc with a Mouth takes a turn for the twisted in a weekly horror comic like no other…

The book starts with Deadpool his killing heroes and villains alike. A newscaster reviews the terror that has been going on since book and we can see corpses of Ghost Rider, Doctor Doom and Howard the Duck. She stops to think and questions if anyone can stop him.

The scene changes to a fight with Spider-Man and Deadpool fighting above the streets of New York City. Spidey kicks Deadpool off of him and he crashes onto a Yellow Taxi Cab. He heals quickly, gets up and walks over to Spider-Man. He pulls out his gun and shoots Spidey in the head.

He walks away from the scene and the new voice tells him to take things slowly. Deadpool does not listen and decides to go for something huge. In the Avengers Mansion, the Avengers call a meeting and the current roster, including reserve members are as follows; Captain America, Ms. Marvel, Thor, Spider-Woman, Luke Cage, Wolverine and Iron Man. Jarvis runs into the room and tells them that Ant-Man is gone. He recalls him being in his labs worried about missing Pym Particles.

Wolverine sniffs the air. And tells the team that something bad is about to happen. Bombs grow to full size on the table along with the body of Hank Pym and the mansion explodes. Deadpool is among the rubble playing with Ant-Man’s helmet and kills Luke with bombs he snuck into the coffee and smashed Thor with an oversized Mjölnir he grew with the last batch of Pym Particles.

Deadpool then goes to the Grand Canyon where Hulk easily dismembers him. Hulk walks away into a cave and, while asleep, turns into Banner. Deadpool Cuts off his head. Later, family members of heroes hire Taskmaster to kill Deadpool.
name: Part II: Avengers: Assassinated

description:
AVX TIE-IN!

They gather to stop the horrors of the Marvel universe before they happen…

…but the secret group known as the Illuminati failed to stop the Phoenix time and time again.

They come together one last time…but will it be enough?
name: Illuminati Assemble

description:
HULK VS. WOLVERINE!!!

HULK VS. THE THING!!!

The conclusion of STAY ANGRY! What devious plan has Banner been up to? REVEALED HERE!!!!
name: Stay Angry! Conclusion: Riot at the God Complex

description:
Thanos is claiming Earth as his own!

The Avengers and the Guardians of the Galaxy team up to bring the Mad Titan some cosmically-charged pain!
name: Outer Space Antics

description:
ALL-NEW ONGOING SERIES!

When Marvel’s premiere thief sets his sights on his biggest score yet, he may just end up over his head. It’s going to take more than just playing cards and southern charm to get out of this one!

BONUS! Bella Donna is NOT in this issue!
name: Once a Thief..., Part One

description:
Among the secrets she’s stolen: complete specs on Iron Man’s armor!

Nothing says Madripoor in the summer like technological meltdowns, A.I.M., and M.O.D.O.K.
name: M.A.D.A.K. Attack!

description: Artist Becky Cloonan rejoins Brian Wood for a new story arc! Hearing of an impostor committing atrocities in his name, Conan returns to Cimmeria to confront the scoundrel. In the frozen North of Conan’s birth, it is now Bêlit who is out of her element!
name: Border Fury, Part 1

description: The Defenders from the Future hope to set out on the adventure of a lifetime, and only the Fantastic Four can help them get there. But can they?
name: The God Ship

description:
“THE SECOND MASTER” PART TWO OF THREE

Texas Twister! Shooting Star! Red Wolf! Firebird! Living Lightning! The Southwest’s greatest heroes the RANGERS are in Houston to take down the Scarlet Spider!

Has Scarlet Spider gone from Houston’s newest hero to Houston’s most wanted?

The mystery of ROXXON deepens... what has Roxxon found in the Gulf of Mexico?

HINT: It ain’t oil!
name: The Second Master, Part Two

description:
Everything Burns: Prologue!

50th Anniversary Thor Special!

The Aesir/Vanir War! The darkest time in Asgard’s past revealed! A history so dark it was seared from the pages!
name: Everything Burns, Prologue

description: Celebrating 50 Years of the Great Responsibility of his Great powers, The Spider-Man 50th Anniversary Series collects the Webbed Wonder’s greatest heretofore secret history! Spanning from his earliest days as a hero to the heyday of the heralded Big Time era and everything in between, a collection of Marvel Legends, venerated comic creators and awe-inspiring artists shine the spotlight on everything that makes Spider-Man the World’s Greatest Superhero!
name: Monsters! Part One

description:
Can the Spider-Men stop Mysterio?

Peter Parker comes face-to-face with the family he never had!

ONE OF THE MOST POWERFUL MOMENTS IN THE LIVES OF BOTH SPIDER-MEN!!!

concept_credits.name: With Great Power Comes Great Responsibility

first_appearance_concepts.name: With Great Power Comes Great Responsibility

description: Cut off from the world she knows, Rogue struggles to survive in an alien landscape!

The concluding chapter of "Wide Awake!" Jonah Panghammer, bottle imp extraordinaire, had a plan: Ali Baba would find a treasure so rich he could give up thieving. Briar Rose would wake up and be allowed to go home. The Snow Queen would finally realize what her life could be like without the evil empire. And Jonah himself would be free to go his own way for once. Too bad Hadeon the Destroyer showed up to ruin everything.
name: Wide Awake, Chapter Six: A Field Spotter's Guide to True Love

description:
THE SAVAGE SIX TOOK THEIR SHOT – NOW VENOM TAKES HIS!

With his darkest secrets exposed to those he loves, Flash Thompson has one name on his hit list: Jack O’Lantern!

Series co-creator Rick Remender takes his final bow while Declan Shalvey (DARK AVENGERS) joins the book for Flash Thompson’s defining hour as a hero!
name: Father's Day

description:
Discordian cells attack American interests all over the world!

Shock journalist Reed Braxton is turning the public against the Sentinel of Liberty.

But if Reed Braxton is dead, who the heck is that on LIVE television?
name: New World Orders, Part 2

description: Fresh from the pages of Mike Allred's MADMAN: Snap City's favorite heroine is ready for her own crimefighting adventures! With the Atomics boys in outer space, it's up to It Girl to keep the streets safe. Easier said than done: The Skunk, the man who murdered her sister, is out of jail and back to old tricks. Meanwhile, Dr. Flem has a brand new space-time experiment and wants It Girl to be his guinea pig!
name: Dark Streets, Snap City

description:
The return of a menace from the past sets Daredevil, Doctor Strange and the ClanDestine on a collision course!

Continues in this month’s Wolverine Annual #1!
name: A Tourist in Hell

description:
Just when you thought you knew all there was to know about Scott Pilgrim comes Scott Pilgrim Color Hardcover vol. 1: Precious Little Life! The first in a series of brand new hardcover editions, this FULL COLOR, remastered, 6”x9” hardcover presents Scott’s first “evil ex” battle as you’ve never seen it before! Plus, previously unpublished extras and bonus materials make this mighty tome one that’s required reading for Scottaholics everywhere!

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter One: Dating A High Schooler
  • Chapter Two: Do You Know Her?
  • Chapter Three: This One Girl...
  • Chapter Four: Romona Come Closer
  • Chapter Five: Everything's Starting To Get Complicated
name: Precious Little Life

first_appearance_teams.name: The League Of Ramona's Evil Ex-Boyfriends

team_credits.name: The League Of Ramona's Evil Ex-Boyfriends

description: Just in time for the fall presidential election, Mat Johnson, acclaimed writer of INCOGNEGRO, delivers a race-against-time political thriller about a militia group that’s plotting to assassinate the second African- American President of the U.S. In the week leading up to a major campaign speech, the Secret Service discovers that an extremist militia group is plotting to assassinate America’s second African American President. The best chance to avert this crisis is to infiltrate the group using an ex-Special Forces war hero turned conservative media pundit named Ted Akers. While Akers’s politics make him a hero to the right-wing fringe and no friend to the current Administration, he takes the assignment and what follows is an adrenalinefueled race against time to stop a President from dying and a country from being ripped apart.
name: OGN

description: The return of the Thither people has forced an uneasy alliance between John Carter and Gullivar Jones. Fighting side by side, they venture into unknown regions to try to rescue Dejah Thoris and stop the Thither King from using the power of Gullivar's carpet to change the face of Barsoom.

Standalone issue! A momentous event from the past! Ten years after the Big Wet, three feral children with strange powers roam the blighted earth, following a calling none of them understand. And there's no time to wonder - because the new world presents danger at every turn, from wolves to wildmen. How will the children survive… and what terrible event will keep them apart for decades to come?
name: Lovesong For A Dead Child

description:
Know also O Prince, that Thulsa Doom did not go quietly into the night, his spirit endured, weak and horrible and viscous. Free of all humanity, hungering with a primal desire, all his thoughts were bent on but a single purpose, Thulsa Doom wanted to go Home.

Atlantis Ressurrection! When that which sank beneath the waves rises once more, and the Empire of Atlantis remembers its lost glory, can Sonja save the Hyborean nations from slavery and DOOM.

An eager young fanboy wants to be Vampi's new partner, and against her better judgment, she goes with him to a truly unsettling scene: a little town holding a convention for a popular series of vampire books and movies. As the town goes to absurd lengths to profit from fans, a gang of different predators arrives - and they're ravenous!
name: Bloodsucker Dusk

description:
It's a bloody showdown between Dracula, and the Vatican's paramilitary wing, Cestus Dei. Vlad has new tricks up his sleeves, alliances with old gods that make Order and Chaos tremble, and his plans of unholy conquest are on the verge of success.

Of course, Vampirella might have something to say about that.

Commander Sven has sworn to do everything possible to protect his squad from harm, but what he's done now puts everything at risk. Backed into a corner, and determined to expose a traitor to the Alliance, Sven can only tell himself that he had no choice but to break a few rules, and use every dirty trick in the book just to survive. And what he and his team have planned from their next mission, a joint operation with the #616, provides a whole new definition to the word counter-mission. Is one Space Explorers life worth their best and probably only chance to know the truth? "Fearless Leader" turns the corner, speeding towards its foregone conclusion...
name: Fearless Leader 4: The Fix

description: JOIN FAN-FAVORITES MARCELINE THE VAMPIRE QUEEN AND PRINCESS BUBBLEGUM FOR ROCK-FUELED EXCITEMENT IN THIS ADVENTURE TIME MINI-SERIES! Now that Princess Bubblegum is properly prepared to rock, it’s time to meet the band…the groovy ghoulish SCREAM QUEENS! Written and drawn by acclaimed cartoonist Meredith Gran (OCTOPUS PIE) and featuring a back-up story from Faith Erin Hicks, with variant covers by Yuko Ota (JOHNNY WANDER). ADVENTURE TIME #1 and #2 sold out before they hit stores! Don’t miss out!
name: Grumpy Butt

volume.name: Adventure Time: Marceline and the Scream Queens
